---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import wbsImg from '../../assets/wbs.png';
---

<MainLayout title="Work Breakdown Structure">
    <section class="space-y-10">
        <header class="max-w-4xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 mb-3">
                Planning
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Work Breakdown Structure (WBS)
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                A Work Breakdown Structure (WBS) is a hierarchical breakdown of a project into manageable
                components. It clarifies scope, deliverables, and responsibilities by organizing work into
                levels, making it easier to estimate cost, time, and resources.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <img
                    src={wbsImg.src}
                    width={wbsImg.width}
                    height={wbsImg.height}
                    alt="Work Breakdown Structure diagram"
                    class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200"
                    loading="lazy"
            />
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-500">
                Figure: WBS diagram for the “Using cheaper materials” project.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">WBS Table</h2>

            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full border-collapse text-left">
                    <thead>
                    <tr class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-700">
                        <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold border-b border-slate-200">Level</th>
                        <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold border-b border-slate-200">WBS Code</th>
                        <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold border-b border-slate-200">Element Name</th>
                        <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold border-b border-slate-200">Definition</th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="text-slate-700">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Using cheaper materials (dealing with vandalism)</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Reduce vandalism by selecting more durable and less worthy materials (for vandals) for pipes.</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Initiation</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Establishing scope, stakeholders, objectives, risks.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.1.1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Project Charter & Scope Statement</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Defining boundaries and success metrics.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.1.2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Schedule & Budget Baseline</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Establishing the Gantt chart and cost controls.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.1.3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Stakeholder Communications</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Keeping in contact with experts.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.1.4</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Risk Management Plan</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Identifying technical and operational risks.</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Planning</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Developing plans for data analysis, what materials to use, costs.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.2.1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Vandalism Report</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Analysis of damage data from the water provider.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.2.2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Material Benchmarking</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Comparative study of potential materials.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.2.3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Estimate potential cost savings in repair and replacement due to vandalism</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Counting expected costs with new materials and comparing it to the current one.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.2.4</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Compliance & Regulatory Analysis</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Ensuring correct standards.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.2.5</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">End-to-end procurement and contracting process</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Preparation of technical specifications and documentation, internal approvals.</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Execution</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Creating, testing, and finishing technical solutions that meet all the requirements.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.3.1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Conceptual CAD Models</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Initial 3D designs.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.3.2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Digital testing</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Digital Analysis Report.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.3.3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Prototype verification</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Ensuring the internal geometry doesn't cause cavitation or pressure drops.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.3.4</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Final Technical Drawings</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">"Ready-for-Manufacture" blueprints.</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.4</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Control</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Test durability, performance, complete analysis.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.4.1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Testing under real-life conditions</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Standard pressure testing to ensure it functions.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.4.2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Monitoring vandalism of the new product</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Documenting exactly how the part fails under extreme stress or vandalism tests.</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.5</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Closeout</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Finalizing project documents, and closing the project.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.5.1</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Final Prototype Delivery</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Handing over the blueprints to the stakeholders.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">1.5.2</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Technical Documentation Package</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200">Providing the testing results.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3">3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3">1.5.3</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3">Lessons Learned & Closeout Report</td>
                        <td class="px-4 py-3">Archiving project data for the presentation.</td>
                    </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>